{"tid":1947111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃色經濟圈】餐廳人數受限 我們更加需要支持黃店","createTime":"2020-03-28T05:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T14:13:18.000Z","uid":349220,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3ee6dfb1945581203379afa107068e8e0fbca722","tid":1947111,"uid":349220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T05:26:27.000Z","msg":"琴日政府落咗新政策 當中餐飲業既條例有6項 <br />\n其中包括「食肆可用座位不超過正常提供的一半、檯之間至少要有1.5米距離，或有其他分隔安排、每張檯不多於 4 個人」<br />\n食肆、酒吧、咖啡店都要跟隨呢個措施<br />\n相信落咗呢啲措施之後 會少咗好多人去黃店食野/消費<br />\n要兩個星期都無乜生意既話 好多黃店會做唔黎 甚至有機會開始大規模告急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家外賣時 都要選擇幫襯黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我記得沙田有一間酒樓 今次咁樣可能會少咗好多老人家去飲早茶 同埋對酒吧生意都有好大打擊 <br />\n希望大家可以支持下佢 繼續比黃色經濟圈堅持落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/giXz6Fo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgiXz6Fo.png&h=af0155f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CoKVRbF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoKVRbF.png&h=cd045123&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c10f6dbcc4501743680722fdd0e63e7e88ab719","tid":1947111,"uid":349220,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"近期告急黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FF83Z5q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFF83Z5q.jpg&h=f86a291c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AHE6XR6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAHE6XR6.png&h=cec15c8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fpifRb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfpifRb7.png&h=ab2eab0c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0281df2d9404f88da17